  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个健康科技诊断流程图。核心是从实验室分析仪开始，经过诊断引擎的处理。我设想左边是HealthTech_LabAnalyzer作为入口节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "明白了，LabAnalyzer作为起始节点。那它的输出流向哪里？是直接进入诊断引擎吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer",
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，第一步流向HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine，但这里有个细节——诊断引擎内部其实有两层处理。第一层B接收原始数据，第二层C做最终分析。所以B和C都是DiagnosticEngine的实例，只是阶段不同。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine",
        "B",
        "C"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "让我确认一下：您的意思是A→B→C的链式结构，其中B和C都标注为HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine？这样会不会让读者混淆这是同一个组件还是两个实例？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "A",
        "B",
        "C",
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确实容易混淆，但这是有意的设计——表示诊断引擎的流水线阶段。B是数据预处理阶段，C是推理决策阶段。保持从左到右的流向，用LR布局。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "B",
        "C",
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我现在绘制：A[HealthTech_LabAnalyzer]指向B[HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine]，B再指向C[HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine]，整体采用从左到右的布局。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "A",
        "B",
        "C",
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer",
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，我注意到刚才的描述有问题。B和C不应该用方括号，它们实际上是流程中的步骤标记，不是独立的节点实体。让我重新说明：A是带标签的节点，然后流向B，B再流向C，B和C都是DiagnosticEngine的引用。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "A",
        "B",
        "C"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已修正。现在结构是：A作为带方括号的节点标签HealthTech_LabAnalyzer，然后箭头指向B（标注HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine），B再箭头指向C（同样标注HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine）。这样B和C作为流程步骤，都指向诊断引擎这个核心组件。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "A",
        "B",
        "C",
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer",
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    }
